data.description:
This home qualifies for $0 Down and 100% USDA financing!! Ask your realtor and lender how to buy this home with $0 down!! Discover perfection in this 4-bed, 2-bath haven within Midway ISD! Enjoy the luxury of a dual-sided fireplace, seamlessly connecting the living room and kitchen. You will love the open and airy living space that features the shared fireplace, adding sophistication to your daily life. The kitchen, complete with modern appliances and stunning granite countertops, centers as a hub for culinary creations and gatherings. Your primary suite awaits with an oversized walk-in closet and spa-worthy bathroom. Additional bedrooms offer flexibility for guests or work-from-home spaces.  Outside, a shared pond with private access beckons relaxation and the perfect spot to go fishing! But don't overlook the lovely fire pit area to enjoy time outdoors with your family and friends. In addition, this home is conveniently located near Interstate 35, which allows quick access to all of Waco! 

Elevate your lifestyle—explore this enchanting 4-bedroom home today!
